channel.title: New Song Challenge Idea
channel.description: I had this idea the other day. I want to make songs, but based around how I feel an artist sounds like. Kind og like my song "Deep" meant to sound like IVO. So send me your artists, (preferably auxy artists, even if its you) and I will post a song on how I think your music sounds

item.title: New Song Challenge Idea
item.dc:creator: Alone_in_Rome
item.description:
This guy is not Auxy related but he hasn’t blown up despite having a trademark sound. Look up Chad Cooper and listen to his 3 songs: Guilty, Because You Can (Jolene), and Happy Song. He’s really good and I think it could be cool replicating his style of uplifting house/EDM! Totally your call it’s just a suggestion
